{"id":232949487,"title":"目前你覺得最方便的「手機QR code無卡提款」是哪一間!?","content":"首先，2020年  祝大家鼠年「鼠錢鼠到手軟」\n\n最近剛好過年，出門消費幾乎都是不帶現金，使用行動支付居多\n\n過年回家剛好要包紅包，發現目前不少銀行有提供「手機QR code無卡提款」服務\n\n手機按一按，等於金融提款卡，以後錢包可以少掉很多重量\n\n我這次試的剛好是「國泰銀行」的無卡提款服務\n\n\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/yyVKFlu.jpg\n\n\n缺點是:存款好像有上限，我試了存42K，結果說存不了，剛好身上有帶「金融卡」，存了42K，立馬存進去了\n\n目前我知道，台新銀行也有\n\n我會推薦在「超商」「提款 」\n因為「安全&有攝影機」「服務點多」「24HR」\n\n不然就是像全聯\n\n不知各位覺得還有哪幾間服務不錯的無卡提款ATM???\n合作金庫的就有點爛，之前試了靜脈提款服務，跟本一直出現錯誤","excerpt":"首先，2020年  祝大家鼠年「鼠錢鼠到手軟」最近剛好過年，出門消費幾乎都是不帶現金，使用行動支付居多，過年回家剛好要包紅包，發現目前不少銀行有提供「手機QR code無卡提款」服務，手機按一按，等於","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"3bceb81c-574e-4a96-8050-4df56096d0df","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-24T07:26:59.795Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-24T07:26:59.795Z","commentCount":6,"likeCount":4,"tags":[],"topics":["銀行","行動支付","ATM","無卡","投資"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"理財","forumAlias":"money","school":"馬里科帕社區學院","department":"會計系","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":4}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/yyVKFlu.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"9312c416-d163-40be-86a8-1808f52a7a6d","url":"https://i.imgur.com/yyVKFlul.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/yyVKFlul.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/yyVKFlul.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-24T07:26:59.795Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-24T07:26:59.795Z"},{"id":"9312c416-d163-40be-86a8-1808f52a7a6d","url":"http://i.imgur.com/yyVKFlu.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/yyVKFlu","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/yyVKFlul.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-24T07:26:59.795Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-24T07:26:59.795Z"}],"postAvatar":""}